=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30f64a74b25d3effa130764df6182d6aebc2599","tid":423944,"uid":28112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個人覺得兩日一夜都夠玩</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n可以一日係河邊hea下食下野睇下教堂去下朱古力博物館<br />\n一日行下街shopping 去對面岸9行都已經好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dec0c9ac9c6e567cb696fabfeca79febd8e99b4","tid":423944,"uid":8328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"之前去K&ouml;ln探同鬼仔同學，行咗半日佢就話：「係咁㗎啦，科隆無乜嘢睇，係啲人幾好幾nice」<br />\n<br />\n之後去飲咗半日啤酒同食馬肉<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，科隆一間bar只賣一個brand嘅啤酒，各大品牌整體嚟講較清甜。推薦Sion, Gaffel，最正係P&auml;ffgen (得2個地方有，希望你搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"551313d796a6275de892cbdb21c568ea9111fef1","tid":423944,"uid":8328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去K&ouml;ln探個鬼仔同學，行咗半日佢就話：「係咁㗎啦，科隆無乜嘢睇，係啲人幾好幾nice」<br />\n<br />\n之後去飲咗半日啤酒同食馬肉<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，科隆一間bar只賣一個brand嘅啤酒，各大品牌整體嚟講較清甜。推薦Sion, Gaffel，最正係P&auml;ffgen (得2個地方有，希望你搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote>"},{"pid":"10434a1414ee5b52b814132a894cf993f8a656ff","tid":423944,"uid":28112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去K&ouml;ln探個鬼仔同學，行咗半日佢就話：「係咁㗎啦，科隆無乜嘢睇，係啲人幾好幾nice」<br />\n<br />\n之後去飲咗半日啤酒同食馬肉<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，科隆一間bar只賣一個brand嘅啤酒，各大品牌整體嚟講較清甜。推薦Sion, Gaffel，最正係P&auml;ffgen (得2個地方有，希望你搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n日日HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd60fc692047507706ac406b7d74638b1e931d0","tid":423944,"uid":8328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交通方面 基本上我2日都冇搭過車<br />\n全部常去景點都係行到嘅距離 <br />\n同埋好鬼寫意 每條街都有野睇下咁<br />\n所以我個人覺得唔搭車其實都ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n市內地鐵(定係tram?)有時成8至10分鐘一班, 行算啦"},{"pid":"2aa7a7672642456fd67277bf1f56c229e0ed5dbb","tid":423944,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"教堂同朱古力博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間落去波恩睇德國近代史博物館<br />\n講好多東西德時期嘅人同事"},{"pid":"3a5188aa89b67ea803fabf1d345376cf69e27ccd","tid":423944,"uid":51510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"成個西德都無咩野睇, Koln, Frankfurt, Bonn, Dusseldorf 全部都幾悶, 不過整體幾舒服, hea下 relax下唔錯"},{"pid":"237cf79beff0512b3b06263cad7c4104806ab94e","tid":423944,"uid":53911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教堂同朱古力博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間落去波恩睇德國近代史博物館<br />\n講好多東西德時期嘅人同事</blockquote><br />\n個館唔知整到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf844f169acdb02119972d0f25ef1e94b9366bb","tid":423944,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教堂同朱古力博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間落去波恩睇德國近代史博物館<br />\n講好多東西德時期嘅人同事</blockquote><br />\n個館唔知整到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝修緊？<br />\n我已經係7年前去<br />\n但印象仲深刻過其他德國景點"},{"pid":"c2a8c6f05111257b37b8b8f41961d49e80fc386a","tid":423944,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教堂同朱古力博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時間落去波恩睇德國近代史博物館<br />\n講好多東西德時期嘅人同事</blockquote><br />\n個館唔知整到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n裝修緊？<br />\n我已經係7年前去<br />\n但印象仲深刻過其他德國景點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去koln都只係記得朱古力博物館<br />\n仲要有得試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de48bf5436ded3d5e4a0535edb4c7ca29a7783d5","tid":423944,"uid":119263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:14:59.000Z","msg":"教堂好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果次夾岩時間睇波，我朋友無興趣，<br />\n我一條友入去同40000個醉酒德國佬睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過氣氛堅正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecd18f455837efbc853e66280a02fb62065b7f8","tid":423944,"uid":1841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"剛剛去完koln,用左20歐買左個情人鎖鎖係橋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb6f7a61b0c5d43709a0dffaf0239790f4edf4e","tid":423944,"uid":741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/010437_3e35dcb581a4714a90fc12547ed6e929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F010437_3e35dcb581a4714a90fc12547ed6e929.jpg&h=77965f74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/010438_f8a55daf82bc48da6d7bbe4a53ad2194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F010438_f8a55daf82bc48da6d7bbe4a53ad2194.jpg&h=395040c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科隆幾好行，同埋算多野買<br />\nD&uuml;sseldorf 可以唔洗去<br />\n垃圾地方人又閪"},{"pid":"6fa841221af56221c1d6bba60030360608e08587","tid":423944,"uid":20669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前去K&ouml;ln探個鬼仔同學，行咗半日佢就話：「係咁㗎啦，科隆無乜嘢睇，係啲人幾好幾nice」<br />\n<br />\n之後去飲咗半日啤酒同食馬肉<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，科隆一間bar只賣一個brand嘅啤酒，各大品牌整體嚟講較清甜。推薦Sio